notes: The first ever ODI held in Paarl
EA Brandes 5/41, the 4th 5-wickets-in-a-match by a Zimbabwean (all within the past 12 months), and the 2nd for Brandes
The second ODI tie involving these 2 countries. Previous was in the 1993/94 Hero Cup at Indore
Zimbabwe yet to register an ODI win against India after 13 matches

milestones.description: Eddo Brandes has become the top wicket-taker for ZIM in ODIs with 47 wickets, going past Heath Streak's 42
Eddo Brandes has taken the most five-wicket hauls (2) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Charlie Lock's record
Zimbabwe's 1-run win against India is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 2-run win against Sri Lanka
